data.desc:
Equip only to a "Gusto" monster. It cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects. You can only use each of the following effects of "Tailwind of Gusto" once per turn. You can banish this card from your GY and discard 1 WIND monster; add 1 "Gusto" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand. During your Main Phase: You can activate this effect based on the equipped monster's Level/Rank;
● 4 or lower: Special Summon 1 "Gusto" monster from your Deck with a different Type than the equipped monster.
● 5 or higher: Special Summon 1 Level 1 Tuner from your Deck.
